    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/00cf2ed7eb824788fdf426bd3097aceb.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/00cf2ed7eb824788fdf426bd3097aceb.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/30823630a059cd173507983a6273e233.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/30823630a059cd173507983a6273e233.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Escape from Slumberland is an online co-op horror game with up to 4 players. Dodge deadly traps, outwit fiendish monsters, and escape with enough moonbeams to sate an ancient evil’s hunger. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/36bae759e015de584193dc0286ae7cd6.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/36bae759e015de584193dc0286ae7cd6.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/469dbe91ea4b0ea16247778361dd654f.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/469dbe91ea4b0ea16247778361dd654f.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Gather toys from the dream realm  and grind them into moonbeams. Will you chicken out while you’re ahead or venture deeper for secrets that could multiply your haul?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/efdcae595bbf8636d3c295344c25ae0c.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/efdcae595bbf8636d3c295344c25ae0c.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/ee14902afd9eb0fbcf3e723c10cefbf9.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=620 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/ee14902afd9eb0fbcf3e723c10cefbf9.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Help your friends from beyond the grave by bestowing powerful blessings. It could be the difference between certain doom and a miraculous escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/3c88e2b1db549d0ab61ac561ec1cfd69.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/3c88e2b1db549d0ab61ac561ec1cfd69.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/4e638af1f7916a13844dadb3c9ce72c7.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=620 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/4e638af1f7916a13844dadb3c9ce72c7.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Befriend the dream dwellers to gain powerful items and unlock new dreams to explore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/db79452c6d8389d432c527117507e9f4.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/db79452c6d8389d432c527117507e9f4.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/47d2667d591438b4921bf10a092a3721.poster.avif?t=1762543787\" width=620 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011520/extras/47d2667d591438b4921bf10a092a3721.webm?t=1762543787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Dabbling with dark forces, an evil institution will sacrifice anything to control the dream realm, <strong><i>including you!</i></strong> Uncover the truth and break free from the cycle.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
